<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4d66b071-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s60910"><num value="60910">§ 60910.</num><heading> Applicability</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter applies in the case of any cold case murder occurring on or after <date date="1970-01-01">January 1, 1970</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4d66b072-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/164/s11">Pub. L. 117–164, § 11</ref>, <date date="2022-08-03">Aug. 3, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/1361">136 Stat. 1361</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
